#

Spicy Honey Garlic Chicken Thighs

$15.99
520 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

ChickenSweetSpicy

Description

Succulent chicken thighs glazed with a spicy honey-garlic sauce, served with roasted sweet potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Chicken thighs: 4 pieces
  • Honey: 1/4 cup
  • Soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic, minced: 4 cloves
  • Red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • Olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Sweet potatoes: 2 large
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Fresh parsley: for garnish
